<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>DomaHub - Domain Name Rentals</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/min/main_index.min.css" />
  <meta name="description" content="DomaHub provides domain name rentals at low, affordable prices and flexible time slots. Rent one today!" />
  <%- include("../templates/head_links"); %>
</head>

<body>

  <%- include("../templates/navbar", {user: user}); %>
  <section id="index-img" class="section is-index-img">
    <span></span>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content has-text-centered margin-bottom-25">
        <h1 class="title is-1 is-white">
          Rent out your exceptional domains.
        </h1>
        <h2 class="subtitle is-4 is-white">
          DomaHub is a marketplace for renting domain names by the
          day, week, or month.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <form class="beta-form">
        <div class="control is-grouped-center margin-bottom-0">
          <p class="control margin-right-5">
            <input tabindex="1" class="input is-medium" type="email" name="betaemail" placeholder="Enter your email"/>
          </p>
          <p class="control">
            <button tabindex="1" class="beta-submit button is-primary is-stylish">Sign Up</button>
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="signup-text">We are looking for users
        with exceptional domain names to participate in our closed beta.</p>
      </form>
      <div class="beta-form-success is-hidden">
        <div class="notification has-text-centered is-white">
          <p>You have been put on the waiting list!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="learn-more-arrow">
      <a tabindex="1" href="#decision-section" id="learn-more-button" title="Learn More">
        <span class="icon is-medium is-white">
          <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="decision-section" class="section is-medium-top">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="tabs-box">
        <ul>
          <li>
            <a id="have-domains-tab" class="is-active" tabindex="1" href="#owners" title="Domain Owners">I have domains</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a id="want-domains-tab" tabindex="1" href="#renters" title="Domain Renters">I want domains</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="have-domains-section" class="section is-medium d-owner">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered margin-bottom-50">Listing with DomaHub.</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-5">
          <div class="content margin-bottom-20">
            <h2>What makes a domain name exceptional?</h2>
            <p>
              These are the types of domains that are successful on DomaHub. They provide
              value and usability to other people, businesses, and companies in the world
              throughout the year.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="columns">
            <div class="column">
              <div class="content">
                <p class="heading is-bold is-uppercase">Unique</p>
                <p>
                  Common phrases or words related to
                  holidays, events, emotions, etc.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column">
              <div class="content">
                <p class="heading is-bold is-uppercase">Memorable</p>
                <p>
                  A marketable tag line, slogan, motto, expression,
                  or saying.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="columns">
            <div class="column">
              <div class="content">
                <p class="heading is-bold is-uppercase">Searchable</p>
                <p>
                  Shows up in common keyword searches and
                  has significant traffic.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="column">
              <div class="content">
                <p class="heading is-bold is-uppercase">Versatile</p>
                <p>
                  Can have multiple meanings and use cases
                  for different audiences.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-5 is-offset-1">
          <div class="content box">
            <h2 class="has-text-centered margin-bottom-25">What are the benefits of renting?</h2>
            <ul class="flex-list">
              <li>
                <span class="icon is-accent">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <p>Earns money and creates a new revenue stream from unused domains
                while you wait for buyers</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="icon is-accent">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <p>Reaches new markets and audiences organically through renters who use
                your domain for various purposes</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="icon is-accent">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <p>Increases the likelihood of a sale or buy-out down the road by
                both renters and visitors</p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium d-owner">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-6 is-offset-3">
          <div class="content">
            <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered margin-bottom-50">How it works.</h1>
            <p>
              Our platform introduces your domain to potential renters. We create the listing page,
              set rental terms, manage payments and transactions, and handle the process of
              redirecting renter's content to the domain. This process is detailed below.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-4">
          <div class="content box has-stripe is-1">
            <p class="is-blacklight">Step One</p>
            <div class="step-box">
              <span class="icon is-medium is-bluedarker">
                <i class="fa fa-list-alt"></i>
              </span>
              <h3 class="is-bold">You List Your Domain</h3>
            </div>
            <p>
              Simply create listings by inserting domains into our upload tool.
              Once you have created listings on DomaHub you will have to verify that you own them
              by pointing an A Record to our servers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-4">
          <div class="content box has-stripe is-2">
            <p class="is-blacklight">Step Two</p>
            <div class="step-box">
              <span class="icon is-medium is-bluedarker">
                <i class="fa fa-calendar-check-o"></i>
              </span>
              <h3 class="is-bold">Someone Rents It</h3>
            </div>
            <p>
              We handle the transaction and pay you directly into a bank account you've linked
              with DomaHub after a few business days. The rental is not complete
              until we confirm payment.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-4">
          <div class="content box has-stripe is-3">
            <p class="is-blacklight">Step Three</p>
            <div class="step-box">
              <span class="icon is-medium is-bluedarker">
                <i class="fa fa-share-square-o"></i>
              </span>
              <h3 class="is-bold">We Redirect Web Content</h3>
            </div>
            <p>
              The renter provides a link to some web content they wish to display
              on their new rental. We utilize your domain's A Record pointed to our servers
              to complete the redirection. The renter does not control hosting.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium d-owner">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered">Why list with DomaHub?</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content margin-bottom-25">
        <h3 class="has-text-centered">
          Here are some of DomaHub's best features and benefits.
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-6">
          <div class="slider-box">
            <div class="slider-content">
              <span class="slider-icon icon is-primary is-medium">
                <i class="fa fa-server"></i>
              </span>
              <div class="content slider-text">
                <h3>Never transfer domains</h3>
                <p>
                  You maintain the nameservers.
                </p>
                <a class="slider-learn is-accent">Click to learn more.</a>
              </div>
              <div class="slider-hidden-content margin-right-25 slider-text">
                <p>
                  Your domain never transfers ownership. The renter doesn't get to
                  use their own nameservers. We simply use an A Record to redirect
                  content to the domain rental.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-arrow">
              <span class="icon is-primary">
                <i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="slider-box">
            <div class="slider-content">
              <span class="slider-icon icon is-primary is-medium">
                <i class="fa fa-gears"></i>
              </span>
              <div class="content slider-text">
                <h3>Control pricing and scheduling</h3>
                <p>
                  You have full control over both.
                </p>
                <a class="slider-learn is-accent">Click to learn more.</a>
              </div>
              <div class="slider-hidden-content margin-right-25 slider-text">
                <p>
                  You get to decide the pricing for all of your domains (minimum one USD).
                  You also decide the time rate it is available for: daily, weekly, or monthly.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-arrow">
              <span class="icon is-primary">
                <i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-6">
          <div class="slider-box">
            <div class="slider-content">
              <span class="slider-icon icon is-primary is-medium">
                <i class="fa fa-book"></i>
              </span>
              <div class="content slider-text">
                <h3>Secure rental contracts</h3>
                <p>
                  All rentals are bounded by our terms.
                </p>
                <a class="slider-learn is-accent">Click to learn more.</a>
              </div>
              <div class="slider-hidden-content margin-right-25 slider-text">
                <p>
                  Every rental is subject to our <a href="/terms" class="is-accent">Terms</a>.
                  We reserve the right to remove any inappropriate rental on DomaHub.
                  Additionally, users can flag and report any rentals themselves.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-arrow">
              <span class="icon is-primary">
                <i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="slider-box">
            <div class="slider-content">
              <span class="slider-icon icon is-primary is-medium">
                <i class="fa fa-credit-card"></i>
              </span>
              <div class="content slider-text">
                <h3>Quick and easy payments</h3>
                <p>
                  Get paid immediately and securely.
                </p>
                <a class="slider-learn is-accent">Click to learn more.</a>
              </div>
              <div class="slider-hidden-content margin-right-25 slider-text">
                <p>
                  DomaHub handles all of the payments so you never have to
                  deal directly with money. Get paid directly into your bank
                  account within a few business days.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-arrow">
              <span class="icon is-primary">
                <i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="want-domains-section" class="section is-medium d-renter is-hidden">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered margin-bottom-50">Get the domains that you want.</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-5">
          <div class="content">
            <h2>The perfect domain.</h2>
            <p>
              It sucks when you can't use a domain because it's already registered.
              It sucks even more when the current owner isn't doing anything useful
              with it. With DomaHub, you don't have to settle for a less than perfect
              domain.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="content">
            <h2>Our mission.</h2>
            <p>
              Our goal is to make every unused registered domain available for
              general use at a reasonable price point. We want you to be
              able to rent the domains you want, at the times you need them -
              all without breaking the bank.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-5 is-offset-1">
          <div class="content">
            <h2>Advantages of renting with us.</h2>
            <p>
              Renting with DomaHub is easy. Once you've chosen a domain, select your
              desired time slot(s) and provide a link to your content
              or website. Your domain rental will now redirect to the provided link!
            </p>
            <ul class="margin-top-15">
              <li>
                <span class="icon is-accent">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Gain access to domains that are already registered</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="icon is-accent">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Rent for the exact times that you need</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="icon is-accent">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Pay a fraction of the cost of buying</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="icon is-accent">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Start displaying your content immediately</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium d-renter is-hidden">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered margin-bottom-50">How it works.</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="columns flex-column-mobile">
        <div class="column is-5 is-offset-1 order-2-mobile">
          <figure class="image has-shadow is-real-ratio">
            <img src="/images/main/listing-capture.jpg" />
          </figure>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-4 order-1-mobile">
          <div class="content">
            <h2>1. Browse Listings</h2>
            <p>
              Browse any of our verified domain listings.
              Each listing has its own dedicated page that displays various
              relevant statistics and information.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-4 is-offset-2">
          <div class="content">
            <h2>2. Select Dates</h2>
            <p>
              Once you've found your domain, confirm your rental dates
              directly on the listing's page. Make sure you select the right
              dates! You won't be able to change them after checking out.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-5">
          <figure class="image has-shadow is-real-ratio">
            <img src="/images/main/date_selection.gif" />
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns flex-column-mobile">
        <div class="column is-5 is-offset-1 order-2-mobile">
          <figure class="image-stack">
            <img src="/images/main/stack-img-3.jpg" alt="" />
            <img src="/images/main/stack-img-2.jpg" alt="" />
            <img src="/images/main/stack-img-1.jpg" alt="" />
          </figure>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-4 order-1-mobile">
          <div class="content">
            <h2>3. Redirect Content</h2>
            <p>
              Prior to checkout, you will have an option to provide a link
              to whatever web content you wish to redirect to your new domain
              rental. You may provide it at that time, or enter it later in your
              <a class="is-accent" href="/profile/myrentals">rentals page</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium is-lighter">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column">
          <div class="content has-text-centered">
            <h1 class="title is-2">Have any questions?</h1>
            <h3>
              Feel free to send us a message or explore the FAQ!
            </h2>
            <div class="button-wrapper">
              <a id="chat-with-us-button" tabindex="1" class="button is-primary is-stylish">
                <span class="icon">
                  <i class="fa fa-commenting"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Chat with Us</span>
              </a>
              <a tabindex="1" class="button is-accent is-stylish" href="/faq" target="_blank">
                <span class="icon">
                  <i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Explore FAQ</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

    <%- include("../templates/footer"); %>
    <%- include("../templates/js_scripts"); %>
    <script src="/js/routes/main/main_index_logic.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  </body>
</html>
